Being vulnerable with someone that constantly hurts you isn’t easy to do, especially when that disappointment comes from a parent. And I realize change must go both ways and not everyone is open to it. But instead of carrying that resentment around, have you considered reasons they might be worthy of your forgiveness? Even if it doesn’t mend the relationship right away, you’ve at least made the effort to start a new chapter. And this includes loving them from a distance if that’s your only option. With the support of Iyanla, this young lady was finally able to tell her mom what was on her heart. Her mother had no idea she was carrying this weight, now that she does, the healing can begin. 💙💜 #LetsTalk What is the ONE thing you haven’t said to the person that hurt you? What is ONE thing they did that you are willing to forgive? 💙 💜 #Iyanla #Forgiveness #SingleMothers #Oprah #Own #TagAFriend **Turn on your notification**Subscribe to my website for NEW content coming soon!
